data.description: Well cared for home with easy living and low maintenance awaits you! This home is owner occupied and has been updated with new AC, new water heater, new interior paint, remodeled bathrooms, newer kitchen appliances, new garage door, & a new sprinkler control box that can be ran from your phone. This home also offers a large pantry, walk-in master closet, ring doorbell, gorgeous concrete stamped floors, a large yard, & a storage shed. The back portion of the deeper side of the garage has been finished with a partition wall. The wall could easily be removed and returned to garage space, or left up and used for an office, workout area, hobby space, or extra storage, etc.
